# Abort crawl then resume

* Crawl a 1 million list item sharepoint site collection fully. Note how many documents you indexed at the end.
* Clear the data source.
* Crawl the sharepoint site collection fully again. Note how many documents you indexed at the end.
  * Assert the number of documents is the same as first crawl.
* Crawl the sharepoint site collection again but this time abort the crawl and resume 3 times throughout, then let it finish.
  * Assert the number of documents is the same as first and second crawl.
  * Assert resume doesn't take an absorbant amount of time to take place.
